      • addScroler

        public void addScroler(ElementButton btn,
                       int value)
        Description copied from interface: ElementList
        Adds to an ElementButton a listener to scroll through this element. The value to scroll forwards by clicking the button can be specified. If the user shiftclicks the button, the value will be multiplied by 2. You can also set the value to a number smaller than 0 to scroll backwards through this element by clicking the button.
        Specified by:

        Parameters:
